snippet.title: Amber Heard and Elon Musk continue to rekindle their romance
snippet.description:
Amber Heard and Elon Musk continue to rekindle their romance.
Despite insisting they are “just friends,” Amber Heard and Elon Musk continue to rekindle their romance.

They were spotted together over the holidays in Chile and visiting Easter Island.

The two began dating early last year, then split in August, with Musk telling Rolling Stone that he was “in severe emotional pain . . . I was really in love, and it hurt bad. Well, she broke up with me more than I broke up with her, I think.”

But since then, they have been spotted twice in LA, first sharing breakfast, then more recently kissing outside a restaurant.
